quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  63,9,"O you who believe! Let not your wealth, or your children, divert you from the remembrance of Allah; and whoever does that, these are the losers"
  63,10,"And spend out of what We have given you before death comes to any of you, lest he should say, \"My Lord! Why did you not respite me for a little while longer, so that I could have given alms and been of the doers of good deeds"
  63,11,But Allah grants not respite to a soul when its appointed term has come and Allah is Aware of what you do